nts)\n*''[[Goober and the Ghost Chasers]]'' (1973\u20131975)\n*''[[Jeannie (TV series)|Jeannie]]'' (1973\u20131975)\n*''[[Partridge Family 2200 A.D.]]'' (1974\u20131975) (re-titled ''The Partridge Family in Outer Space'')\n*''[[The Pebbles and Bamm-Bamm Show]]'' (1971\u20131972)\n*''[[Yogi's Gang]]'' (1973)\n\nThe six series were repackaged from their original half-hour formats into multi-part [[Serial (radio and television)|serialized]] segments which were introduced by Fred on a daily basis (via [[voice-over]]s on brief bumper clips shown in-between segments). The opening title sequence was a composite, using clips from the openings of the various series, along with a new title theme song. Like many animated series created by Hanna-Barbera in the 1970s, the show contained an inferior [[Laugh track#Making their own|laugh track created by the studio]].\n\n==Voice cast==\n* [[Henry Corden]] \u2013 [[Fred Flintstone]] (Host), [[The Hillbilly Bears|Paw Rugg]], Dr. Bigot (''Yogi's Gang'')\n* [[Josh Albee]] \u2013 Freddy, Jimmy (''Yogi's Gang'')\n* [[Sherry Alberoni]] \u2013 Laurie Partridge (''The Partridge Family in Outer Space'')\n* [[Julie Bennett]] \u2013 [[Cindy Bear]] (''Yogi's Gang'')\n* [[Joe Besser]] \u2013 Babu (''Jeannie'')\n* [[Mel Blanc]] \u2013 [[Barney Rubble]], [[Dino (The Flintstones)|Dino]], Zonk, Stub (''The Pebbles and Bamm-Bamm Show'', ''The Flintstone Comedy Hour'')\n* [[Danny Bonaduce]] \u2013 Danny Partridge (''Goober and the Ghost Chasers'', ''The Partridge Family in Outer Space'')\n* [[Tom Bosley]] \u2013 Commadore Phineas P. Fibber (''Yogi's Gang'')\n* [[Daws Butler]] \u2013 [[Yogi Bear]], [[Huckleberry Hound]], [[Quick Draw McGraw]], [[Snagglepuss]], [[Wally Gator]], [[Peter Potamus]], [[Augie Doggie and Doggie Daddy|Augie Doggie]], [[Hokey Wolf]], [[Lippy the Lion & Hardy Har Har|Lippy the Lion]], [[Baba Looey]] (''Yogi's Gang'')\n* [[Tommy Cook (actor)|Tommy Cook]] \u2013 S. Melvin Farthinghill (''Jeannie'')\n* [[Suzanne Crough]] \u2013 Tracy Partridge (''Goober and the Ghost Chasers'', ''The Partridge Family in Outer Space'')\n* [[Jerry Dexter]] \u2013 Ted (''Goober and the Ghost Chasers'')\n* [[Susan Dey]] \u2013 Laurie Partridge (''Goober and the Ghost Chasers'')\n* [[Micky Dolenz]] \u2013 Wonderful Wayne, Spotless Sam (''The Partridge Family in Outer Space'')\n* Carl Esser \u2013 Fabian (''The Pebbles and Bamm-Bamm Show'', ''The Flintstone Comedy Hour'')\n* [[Brian Forster]] \u2013 Chris Partridge (''Goober and the Ghost Chasers'', ''The Partridge Family in Outer Space'')\n* [[Joan Gerber]] \u2013 Shirley Partridge (''The Partridge Family in Outer Space'')\n* [[Virginia Gregg]] \u2013 Gossipy Witch of the West (''Yogi's Gang'')\n* [[Mark Hamill]] \u2013 Corey Anders (''Jeannie'')\n* [[Jo Ann Harris]] \u2013 Tina (''Goober and the Ghost Chasers'')\n* [[Gay Autterson|Gay Hartwig]] \u2013 [[Betty Rubble]], Wiggy, Cindy (''The Pebbles and Bamm-Bamm Show'', ''The Flintstone Comedy Hour'')\n* [[Bob Hastings]] \u2013 Henry Glopp (''Jeannie'')\n* [[Rose Marie]] \u2013 Lotta Litter (''Yogi's Gang'')\n* [[Mitzi McCall]] \u2013 Penny (''The Pebbles and Bamm-Bamm Show'', ''The Flintstone Comedy Hour'')\n* Chuck McLenan \u2013 Keith Partridge (''The Partridge Family in Outer Space'')\n* [[Julie McWhirter]] \u2013 Jeannie (''Jeannie''),  Marion (''The Partridge Family in Outer Space'')\n* [[Allan Melvin]] \u2013 [[Magilla Gorilla]], Mr. Sloppy, Mr. Neat, Professor Haggling (''Yogi's Gang'')\n* [[Don Messick]] \u2013 [[Boo-Boo Bear]], [[Ranger Smith]], [[Touch\u00e9 Turtle and Dum Dum|Touch\u00e9 Turtle]], [[Atom Ant]], [[Squiddly Diddly]], Mayor of Smog City (''Yogi's Gang''), Schleprock (''The Pebbles and Bamm-Bamm Show'', ''The Flintstone Comedy Hour'')\n* [[Jay North]] \u2013 [[Bamm-Bamm Rubble]] (''The Pebbles and Bamm-Bamm Show'', ''The Flintstone Comedy Hour'')\n* [[Alan Reed]] \u2013 [[Fred Flintstone]] (''The Pebbles and Bamm-Bamm Show'', ''The Flintstone Comedy Hour'')\n* [[Ronnie Schell]] \u2013 Gilly (''Goober and the Ghost Chasers'')\n* [[Hal Smith (actor)|Hal Smith]] \u2013 J. Wanton Vandal, Smiley the Hobo (''Yogi's Gang'')\n* [[John Stephenson (actor)|John Stephenson]] \u2013 [[Augie Doggie and Doggie Daddy|Doggie Daddy]], [[Lippy the Lion & Hardy Har Har|Hardy Har Har]], Mr. Cheerful, Greedy Genie, Hilarious P. Prankster, Envy Brother #2, Captain Swashbuckle Swipe, Fumbo Jumbo the Masked Avenger, Mr. Hothead, Professor Bickering (''Yogi's Gang''), Mr. Slate, Noodles (''The Pebbles and Bamm-Bamm Show'', ''The Flintstone Comedy Hour''), Haji (''Jeannie''), Reuben Kincaid (''The Partridge Family in Outer Space'')\n* Mickey Stevens \u2013 [[Pebbles Flintstone]] (''The Flintstone Comedy Hour'')\n* [[Sally Struthers]] \u2013 [[Pebbles Flintstone]] (''The Pebbles and Bamm-Bamm Show'')\n* [[Jean Vander Pyl]] \u2013 [[Wilma Flintstone]] (''The Pebbles and Bamm-Bamm Show'', ''The Flintstone Comedy Hour''), [[The Hillbilly Bears|Maw Rugg]] (''Yogi's Gang'')\n* [[Janet Waldo]] \u2013 Mrs. Anders (''Jeannie'')\n* [[Lennie Weinrib]] \u2013 Smokestack Smog (''Yogi's Gang''), Moonrock, Bronto (''The Pebbles and Bamm-Bamm Show'', ''The Flintstone Comedy Hour''), Jolly Joe (''The Partridge Family in Outer Space'')\n* [[Frank Welker]] \u2013 Orbit, Veenie (''The Partridge Family in Outer Space'')\n* [[Jesse White (actor)|Jesse White]] \u2013 Peter D. Cheater (''Yogi's Gang'')\n* [[Paul Winchell]] \u2013 Goober (''Goober and the Ghost Chasers''), Sheik of Selfishness (''Yogi's Gang'')\n\n==Weekly airing schedule==\nThe following segments were broadcast in [[parity (mathematics)|odd weeks]]:\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Monday !! Tuesday !! Wednesday !! Thursday !! Friday\n|-\n| ''Jeannie'' <small>[Part 1]</small><br>''Yogi's Gang'' <small>[Part 1]</small> || ''Jeannie'' <small>[Part 2]</small><br>''Yogi's Gang'' <small>[Part 2]</small> ||  ''Goober and the Ghost Chasers'' <small>[Part 1]</small><br>''Yogi's Gang'' <small>[Part 3]</small> || ''Goober and the Ghost Chasers'' 