ewsnetwork.com/news/2014-03-25/aoi-yuki-emiri-kato-ai-kayano-join-keroro-cast|website=[[Anime News Network]]|date=March 25, 2014|accessdate=September 12, 2016}}</ref> Black Star, Monaka\n|-\n|''[[The Seven Deadly Sins (manga)|The Seven Deadly Sins]]'' || Diane<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Sword Art Online|Sword Art Online II]]'' || Yuuki Konno<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Yu-Gi-Oh! Arc-V]]'' || Mieru Hochun<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"23\" | 2015 || ''[[Aria the Scarlet Ammo|Aria the Scarlet Ammo AA]]'' || Kirin Shima<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Case Closed]]'' || Funako Nakai<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Chaos Dragon]]'' || Shaddy<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Dog Days (Japanese TV series)|Dog Days\"]]'' || Couvert Eschenbach Pastillage<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Gangsta.]] || Nina<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[A Simple Thinking About Blood Type|Ketsuekigata-kun! 2]]'' || Type A-chan<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[A Simple Thinking About Blood Type|Ketsuekigata-kun! 3]]'' || Type A-chan\n|-\n|''[[My Teen Romantic Comedy SNAFU TOO!]]'' || Komachi Hikigaya\n|-\n|''[[One-Punch Man]]'' || Tornado of Terror<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Onsen Y\u014dsei Hakone-chan]]'' || Goura<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Overlord (novel series)|Overlord]]'' || Clementine<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Rokka: Braves of the Six Flowers]]'' || Fremy Speeddraw<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Senki Zessh\u014d Symphogear|Senki Zessh\u014d Symphogear GX]]'' || Hibiki Tachibana<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Seraph of the End]]'' || Krul Tepes<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[List of Tantei Opera Milky Holmes episodes#Tantei Kageki Milky Holmes TD (2015)|Tantei Kageki Milky Holmes TD]]'' || Carroll Dodgson<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[The Asterisk War]]'' || Meeko Yanase<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[Tokyo Ghoul|Tokyo Ghoul \u221aA]]'' || Kurona Yasuhisa<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\n|''[[World Break: Aria of Curse for a Holy Swordsman]]'' || Shizuno Urushibara<ref name=\"vadb\"/>\n|-\